特地从江苏赶来上海买黄金、置办年货，王小姐向记者透露，“买了一颗2克的小金珠，一枚金戒指，还给家里人买了生肖产品，图个过年好彩头。” 卖疯了！有人特意从外地赶来上海，有金店一天卖出1000多根金条"},"attached_info":"Cj8I8NiShozY97EuEAMaCTEwNTQyNjY0MiDo16quBjAAOExACHIJNjQ0MTcwNDczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"52 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-43d23da43df593d28fdcc134222e587b_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1708013783.188157","card_id":"Q_644342187","target":{"id":644342187,"title":"2 月电影票房破 70 亿，《热辣滚烫》《飞驰人生2》《熊出没·逆转时空》分列前三，哪些信息值得关注？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/644342187","type":"question","created":1707918112,"answer_count":180,"follower_count":317,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[68,99,1400,1740,5582],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"据灯塔专业版数据，截至2月15日19时20分，2024年2月总票房破70亿。2024年2月电影票房破70亿 | 每经网 2024年2月总票房破60亿 据猫眼专业版数据，2月14日18时55分，2024年2月总票房破60亿，《热辣滚烫》《飞驰人生2》《熊出没·逆转时空》分列2月票房榜前三位。"},"attached_info":"CkAI8NiShozY97EuEAMaCTEwNTQ2NDg3NyCghrOuBjAAOL0CQAlyCTY0NDM0MjE4N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"32 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8f6afc735f1369ed827c4ec2e5b6366a_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1708013783.188889","card_id":"Q_644079037","target":{"id":644079037,"title":"以军对加沙南部发动海陆空全方位打击，超 100 人死亡，这意味着什么？未来局势将如何走？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/644079037","type":"question","created":1707706664,"answer_count":244,"follower_count":512,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1234,3115,4621,154121,1369346],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端 据巴勒斯坦通讯社报道，当地时间12日凌晨，以军对加沙地带南部城市拉法及周边地区发动海陆空全方位打击，目前造成死亡人数已超过100人，另